[I] A fully transparent multilingual content solution for zope/plone

[T] I18NLayer provides a fully transparent virtual layer above multiple content objects.
[T] Each content object represents a special language translation. By use of automatic
[T] or manual language negotiation the I18NLayer objects delivers the matching language
[T] to the user.

